{"tid":1881421,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又嚟回馬槍：反對罷工，然後今日醫管局要進一步減少非緊急服務","createTime":"2020-02-15T14:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T05:51:29.000Z","uid":77905,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d7d10fa9258d733b43e71aa9e005b33b595e47b7","tid":1881421,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:06:44.000Z","msg":"醫管局：反對罷工<br />\n葉劉淑儀：政府應立法禁止罷工<br />\n<br />\n今日：醫院管理局總行政經理何婉霞表示，有國家已把相關物資列為戰略物品，並限制出口，令局方採購相當困難，但已加大加快採購程序。醫管局總行政經理張子峯表示，醫管局在下周一起，<span style=\"color: red;\">將進一步減少非緊急及非必要服務，包括延後部分專科門診、專職醫療門診及普通科門診的覆診</span>，但會維持緊急及迫切性服務。部分原定未來14日內覆診或預約入院的病人將延期。<span style=\"color: red;\">醫管局預計，平均每日將有1萬名病人受影響。</span>"},{"pid":"d3b1c801c086664a76ea252a3f8f8d850ee56033","tid":1881421,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:08:56.000Z","msg":"跪求大家唔好放棄國際線<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=uD1rvIJwXfBqs1i1iclFx8jT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=0bf8244b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"cdab548496e2984514837ddc946e621969fa1962","tid":1881421,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3b1c801c086664a76ea252a3f8f8d850ee56033","tid":1881421,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:08:56.000Z","msg":"跪求大家唔好放棄國際線<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me